WEBVTT

00:00:57.899 --> 00:01:00.155
free enterprise and free trade.

00:01:00.686 --> 00:01:06.213
You've watched Ronald Reagan's
farewell address over and over,

00:01:06.237 --> 00:01:08.527
and you cry every time --

00:01:08.551 --> 00:01:09.672
(Laughter)

00:01:09.696 --> 00:01:13.683
he gets to the part about
the shining city on the hill,

00:01:13.707 --> 00:01:16.684
and how if the city had to have walls,

00:01:16.708 --> 00:01:18.890
the walls had doors --

00:01:18.914 --> 00:01:22.411
doors to let in those yearning
to breathe free.

00:01:23.525 --> 00:01:28.242
You get goosebumps when you think
of him telling Mr. Gorbachev

00:01:28.266 --> 00:01:30.646
to tear down his wall.